Dwivedi, Sanjai K., Def Res \& Dev Org, CEPTEM, Delhi 110054, India.
Singh, Harvinder, Jaypee Univ Informat Technol, Waknaghat 173215, Solan, India.},
  affiliations = {Defence Research \& Development Organisation (DRDO); Defence Institute
of High Altitude Research (DIHAR); Defence Research \& Development
Organisation (DRDO); Jaypee University of Information Technology},
